title: Hennessy stays low-key as Mirkarimi perseveres in sheriff’s race
text:
Photo: Lea Suzuki, The Chronicle Sheriff Ross Mirkarimi speaks during a news conference at San Francisco City Hall on Friday, July 10, 2015 in San Francisco, Calif. Sheriff Ross Mirkarimi speaks during a news conference at San...
In his uphill attempt to win re-election, San Francisco Sheriff Ross Mirkarimi has billed himself as the outsider who is willing to buck the status quo and independent of the insular loyalty endemic to the law enforcement establishment.
